---
title: Smoky Double Beef Cheeseburgers with Caramelized Onions
description: This classic diner meal becomes next-level delicious with the addition of smoky flavours courtesy of smoked paprika and garlic-dusted potato wedges and a creamy BBQ mayo! Topped with caramelized onions, these burgers are sure to earn a place among your family’s favourites

